ers. Professional experience in a motion graphic production design environment you will oversee the production of a wide variety of motion graphic solutions that support sales, marketing campaigns, and internal/external presentations to meet our companys global business needs. You will collaborate within the team to research and implement current motion graphic development and implementation strategies to create a wide variety of technical animations. You will work directly with subject matter experts to create visually accurate semiconductor manufacturing technical depictions and content layout. You are self-motivated and fast-paced, and you love being a part of a team. You understand brand and design guideline systems, and you have a passion and expertise for creative solutions Primary Skills/Abilities: Cinema 4D After Effects InDesign PowerPoint Illustrator Photoshop Project management (Write) Project file management 2D / 3D production skills including materializing, animating, lighting, rendering, and compositing Basic video editing and encoding Basic audio capturing, editing, mixing, and mastering Graphic design layout, and printing experience a plus Ability to quickly generate multiple initial concepts and develop them into viable motion graphic design solutions in a fast-paced, deadline-driven environment Excellent team player. Proactive in learning new skills and receptive to feedback Strong project management, organizational, and interpersonal skills Portfolio or demo reel of relevant work is required Brand: Palo Alto Alvarado Concepts Address: 924 W. Colfax Ave., Ste. 203 Denver, CO - 80204 Property Description: 1-Corporate - W. Colfax Ave - Denver, CO Property Number: 1 "
